# FVWM-Crystal version

# Setup colorsets
Read $./Colorsets

DestroyDecor recreate WindowDecoration
AddToDecor WindowDecoration

+ TitleStyle InActive Colorset $[cs-window-inactive]
+ TitleStyle Active Colorset $[cs-window-active]
+ TitleStyle Centered
+ TitleStyle -- flat
+ TitleStyle Height 22

+ BorderStyle -- HiddenHandles
+ BorderStyle -- Flat

# Close
+ ButtonStyle 1 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray.png
+ ButtonStyle 1 ActiveUp Pixmap $./button-gray-red.png
+ ButtonStyle 1 ActiveDown Pixmap $./button-gray.png

# Close
+ ButtonStyle 2 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray.png
+ ButtonStyle 2 ActiveUp Pixmap $./button-gray-red.png
+ ButtonStyle 2 ActiveDown Pixmap $./button-gray.png

# Maximize
+ ButtonStyle 4 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray.png
+ ButtonStyle 4 ActiveUp Pixmap $./button-gray-green.png
+ ButtonStyle 4 ActiveDown Pixmap $./button-gray.png

# Options
+ ButtonStyle 6 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray.png
+ ButtonStyle 6 ActiveUp Pixmap $./button-gray-violet.png
+ ButtonStyle 6 ActiveDown Pixmap $./button-gray.png

# Arrows
+ ButtonStyle 8 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray.png
+ ButtonStyle 8 ActiveUp Pixmap $./button-gray-blue.png
+ ButtonStyle 8 ActiveDown Pixmap $./button-gray.png

+ ButtonStyle All -- UseTitleStyle
+ ButtonStyle All -- flat

Style * HandleWidth 1, BorderWidth 1
Style * Colorset                $[cs-window-inactive], \
        BorderColorset          $[cs-window-inactive], \
        HilightColorset         $[cs-window-active], \
        HilightBorderColorset   $[cs-window-active]

Style * Font "xft:Tahoma:pixelsize=14:minspace=True"

Style * UseDecor WindowDecoration

# Setup button functions
Include components/decorations/Buttons-fvwm-crystal

